Available Tools: create_subscription | cancel_subscription | pause_subscription | update_plan | get_subscription
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "customer_id": "string", "plan_id": "string", "trial_days": number }
Response Schema: { "subscription_id": "string", "status": "active|canceled|paused|trialing", "plan": "string", "current_period_end": "string" }
---
Question: Suspend the subscription for client cust_5091 right now because of a payment failure.
Call: { "func_call": "pause_subscription", "customer_id": "cust_5091", "plan_id": "plan_essential_monthly", "trial_days": 0 }
Response: { "subscription_id": "sub_10293", "status": "paused", "plan": "plan_essential_monthly", "current_period_end": "2024-06-14T00:00:00Z" }

Question: Transition customer cust_6723 from the lite plan to the business plan instantly, calculating the prorated amount.
